LINK: https://leetcode.com/problems/actors-and-directors-who-cooperated-at-least-three-times/description/?envType=problem-list-v2&envId=v9r4nua2
TYPE: Easy

==> My approach:
import pandas as pd

def actors_and_directors(actor_director: pd.DataFrame) -> pd.DataFrame:
    # Get actor-direct pair that occurred more than 3 times
    return actor_director.groupby(['actor_id', 'director_id']).size().reset_index(name='pair_count').query('pair_count >= 3')[['actor_id', 'director_id']]
